       S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN.
      *@1 초기화

      *@1.1 출력영역확보 파라미터 및 결과코드 초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-AREA
                         XIJICOMM-IN
                         XDJL4272-IN
                         XZUGOTMY-IN

      *@1.2 출력영역 확보
           #GETOUT       YPJL4272-CA

      *@1.3 COMMON AREA SETTING 공통IC프로그램 호출
      *    KB-PIN
           MOVE YNJL4272-KB-PIN        TO AACOM-CUST-IDNFR

           #DYCALL IJICOMM YCCOMMON-CA XIJICOMM-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과 확인
           IF COND-XIJICOMM-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XIJICOMM-R-ERRCD
                     XIJICOMM-R-TREAT-CD
                     XIJICOMM-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  입력값검증
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-VALIDATION-RTN.
      *@2 입력값검증

      *@2.1 처리구분CHECK
      *@실행조건:YNJL4272-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01 AND CO-CHA-02
      *@처리내용:처리구분 01,02 아닐경우 오류처리한다
      *@에러메시지:처리구분 오류입니다
      *@조치메시지:전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
           IF YNJL4272-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01 AND
                                         CO-CHA-02
              #ERROR CO-B3000070 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF
           .
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.
